(ns o2w.api.data
  (:require [reagent.core :as r]
            [reagent.impl.component :refer [component-name]]
            [o2w.api.impl :as impl]
            [ajax.core :as ajax]))

(def remote-data* (r/atom {}))

(defn component-id [c]
  (let [{:keys [id]} (r/argv c)]
    (or id (component-name c))))

(defn get-data [c k] (get-in @remote-data* [(component-id c) k]))
(defn set-data [c k value] (swap! remote-data* assoc-in [(component-id c) k] value))

(defn cancel-timeout [c]
  (when-let [timeout (get-data c :timeout)]
    (js/clearTimeout timeout)))

(defn save-params [c argv]
  (swap! remote-data* assoc-in [(component-id c) :argv] (select-keys argv [:params :endpoint])))

(defn params-changed? [c argv]
  (if-let [old (get-data c :argv)]
    (not= old (select-keys argv [:params :endpoint]))
    true))

(defn load-data!
  [c atom {:keys [endpoint params refresh loading? error interceptor ok base-url headers
                  params-interceptor]
           :as   args
           :or   {interceptor identity}}]

  (let [request        (r/cursor remote-data* [(component-id c) :request])
        set-timeout    (fn [] (when refresh
                               (cancel-timeout c)
                               (set-data c :timeout (js/setTimeout #(load-data! c atom args) (* 1000 refresh)))))
        request-params (cond-> {:params  (if params-interceptor (params-interceptor params) params)
                                :request request
                                :error   #(do
                                            (set-timeout)
                                            (when loading? (reset! loading? false))
                                            (if error (error % atom) ((:error @impl/config) %)))
                                :ok      #(do
                                            (set-timeout)
                                            (reset! atom (interceptor %))
                                            (when ok (ok % atom))
                                            (when loading? (reset! loading? false)))}
                         params-interceptor (assoc :interceptor identity)
                         base-url           (merge {:base-url base-url})
                         headers            (merge {:headers headers}))]

    (impl/req endpoint request-params)))

(defn load-remote-data [c atom {:keys [cache? reset? loading?]
                                :as   args
                                :or   {cache? true}}]
  (when (or (not cache?) (not @atom) (params-changed? c args))
    (when reset? (reset! atom nil))
    (when loading? (reset! loading? true))
    (load-data! c atom args)
    (save-params c args)))

(defn cancel-load-data [c]
  (cancel-timeout c)
  (when-let [request (get-data c :request)]
    (ajax/abort request)))

(defn source [atom {:keys [id] :as argv}]
  (r/create-class {:displayName                  (or id "remote-data")
                   :component-did-mount          (fn [this] (load-remote-data this atom argv))
                   :component-will-receive-props (fn [this new-argv] (load-remote-data this atom (last new-argv)))
                   :reagent-render               (fn [atom params])
                   :component-will-unmount       (fn [this] (cancel-load-data this))}))
